  "attachmentHtml": "\n<p><strong>PC Number: </strong>2003-0110<br></p><p><strong>Date: </strong>2003-01-30</p><hr><p>   </p><p style=\"line-height: 0.36in\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Whereas vacancies exist in the officer establishment numbers prescribed by Treasury Board under subsection 6(2) of the <em>Royal Canadian Mounted Police Act</em>;</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.36in\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.36in\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Therefore, Her Excellency the Governor General in Council, on the recommendation of the Solicitor General of Canada, pursuant to paragraph 6(3)(<em>c</em>) of the <em>Royal Canadian Mounted Police Act</em>, hereby appoints, by way of promotion, the officers of the Royal Canadian Mounted Police named in the schedule hereto to the ranks shown, effective upon the date indicated therein.</p> <br> <p style=\"line-height: 0.36in\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Attendu qu’il existe des vacances au sein de l’effectif des officiers dont le nombre est fixé par le Conseil du Trésor conformément au paragraphe 6(2) de la <em>Loi sur la Gendarmerie royale du Canada</em>,</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.36in\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.36in\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;À ces causes, sur recommandation du solliciteur général du Canada et en vertu de l’alinéa 6(3)<em>c</em>) de la <em>Loi sur la Gendarmerie royale du Canada</em>, Son&nbsp;Excellence la Gouverneure générale en conseil, par voie de promotion, nomme les officiers de la Gendarmerie royale du Canada dont le nom figure à l’annexe ci-jointe aux grades indiqués, à compter de la date qui y est précisée.</p> <br> <p style=\"text-align: center; margin-left: -0.8125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">SCHEDULE</p> <p style=\"margin-left: -0.8125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-indent: -0.5in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; text-indent: -0.5in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Promotion effective November&nbsp;30,&nbsp;2002</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">To the rank of Superintendent</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">Inspector William Bruce Adams</p> <p style=\"margin-left: -0.8125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-indent: -0.5in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; text-indent: -0.5in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Promotion effective December&nbsp;27,&nbsp;2002</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">To the rank of Superintendent</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">Inspector Kerry Alan Bennington</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; text-indent: -0.5in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; text-indent: -0.5in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Promotion effective December&nbsp;2,&nbsp;2002</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">To the rank of Superintendent</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">Inspector Richard David Betker</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; text-indent: -0.5in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; text-indent: -0.5in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Promotion effective December&nbsp;9,&nbsp;2002</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">To the rank of Assistant Commissioner</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">Chief Superintendent Marie Claire Lise Blanche Ghyslaine Clément</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; text-indent: -0.5in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; text-indent: -0.5in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Promotion effective November&nbsp;30,&nbsp;2002</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">To the rank of Chief Superintendent</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">Inspector Sandra Mae Marie Marguerite Conlin</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; text-indent: -0.5in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; text-indent: -0.5in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Promotion effective December&nbsp;6,&nbsp;2002</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">To the rank of Assistant Commissioner</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">Chief Superintendent Darrell John Lafosse</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; text-indent: -0.5in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; text-indent: -0.5in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Promotion effective November&nbsp;30,&nbsp;2002</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; margin-left: -0.3125in; margin-right: -0.5in\">To the rank of Chief Superintendent</p> <p style=\"line-height: 0.270001in; margin-left